On every project's index file (Test if needed in other html file), add the <script src="cordova.js"></script>

Get the computer (Server IP) and give to every app



Platform:
  cordova platform add android@6.3.0
  cordova platform add ios

QRCode :
  cordova plugin add phonegap-plugin-barcodescanner

Notification:
  Put the google_services.json file in every project
  cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-firebase@0.1.25 --save
